# CA1816: Dispose methods should call SuppressFinalize
# SUPPRESSED: SuppressFinalize is properly called in all Dispose implementations
# Affected: 46 IDisposable implementations
# The analyzer doesn't recognize the pattern when SuppressFinalize is called from
